OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA grey start this morning,
OL,6,Fespecially in the east. However any
OL,7,Fcloud will quickly burn away to leave
OL,8,Fanother sunny day. Feeling very warm
OL,9,Fin the strong sunshine, although an
OL,10,Feasterly breeze may offer some relief
OL,11,Fin places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining dry and warm
OL,14,Fovernight with plenty of clear skies.
OL,15,FSome patchy cloud however may reform
OL,16,Flater in the night across the east.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAny overnight cloud quickly
OL,19,Fclearing to leave a dry and sunny day
OL,20,Facross the region. Feeling very warm
OL,21,Fonce again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
