OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FLittle
OL,6,Fchanges throughout the middle of the
OL,7,Fweek with the largely dry, settled and
OL,8,Fvery warm weather continuing. A small
OL,9,Fchance of the odd thunderstorm
OL,10,Fdeveloping by Thursday.
